{
  "id": "adv_main_03_05_05",
  "title": "BIG4編1章25話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな……ごめんね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone… I’m sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "渚……ごめん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa… I’m sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4000004132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.2666670799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ここで止まっちゃいけない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t stop here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2666670799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "私は……強くならなきゃいけない。絶対に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I have to become stronger. I have to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1333337466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "garden-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 16.7166670799
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 17.000000415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "あ～あ、言っちゃった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh… I said it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7666670799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "（ねえ、琴乃ちゃん）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Hey‚ Kotono-chan.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3555104573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "（私、琴乃ちゃんと話して）\n（改めて気付いたことがあるんだよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(After talking to you‚)\n(I realized something.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "（私ね、自分もアイドルとして輝きたいって）\n（想いは変わらないけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I know I still want to shine as an idol‚)\n(but…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱり、琴乃ちゃんとずっと一緒に）\n（アイドルを続けたいな、って思ったんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I really want to keep being an idol)\n(with you forever.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "（さっきの琴乃ちゃんが泣いて笑う顔がね）\n（あんまりにも辛くて、でも、綺麗だったんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(When I saw you crying and smiling earlier‚)\n(it was so painful‚ but also so beautiful.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8071267884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "……琴乃ちゃんはやっぱり凄いんだよ\nファンの人達だって知らない顔がまだまだいっぱいある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re amazing‚ Kotono-chan.\nThere are still so many sides to you that your fans don’t know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんは凄いんだぞ、って\nみんなに言いたいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to tell everyone\nhow amazing you are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7167538086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 64.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "でも……ずっと一緒にいようと思ったら\nやっぱり今は一緒にいちゃダメだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… if I want to be with you forever‚\nI can’t be with you right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.8999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "今のままじゃ、琴乃ちゃんを後ろで\n支えるだけになっちゃう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If things stay the same‚ I'll only be able to\nsupport you from behind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "並んで立とうとするなら……\n私も同じくらい輝かなくちゃダメ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I want to stand beside you…\nI have to shine just as brightly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "今は、別々の道を進むことになったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re on different paths now‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.4186810015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが戻って来たくなるくらいの\nグループになればいいんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just need to make our group so good\nthat you’ll want to come back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、この気持ちは琴乃ちゃんに伝えたから\n後はもう、私が頑張るだけだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay. I’ve told you how I feel.\nAll I have to do now is work hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8179080485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "だから今は、これで、いいん……だよね？\n今、は……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it’s okay… for now‚ right?\nFor now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "うっ、うっ……。琴乃、ちゃん、琴乃ちゃん……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sniff‚ sniff… Kotono-chan‚ Kotono-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4999961692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "ここで止まっちゃダメだよね\n私は行くよ、琴乃ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t stop here.\nI’m leaving‚ Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "今は……それぞれの道を進もう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's walk our own paths for now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2213111399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.871950038
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.871950038
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 131.121950038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "（その後、{user}さんは）\n（琴乃ちゃんと何度も話し合った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(After that‚ {user}-san)\n(talked with Kotono-chan many times.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8931044048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.4924037137
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "（だけど琴乃ちゃんの意志は固くて）\n（根気強い説得にも応じなかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But Kotono-chan’s decision was firm‚)\n(and she wouldn’t listen to his persistent persuasion.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.8333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 143.6159863947
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "（沙季ちゃん、すずちゃん、芽衣ちゃんはもちろん）\n（反対した。五人だからやれることがあるはずだ、って）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Of course Saki-chan‚ Suzu-chan‚ and Mei-chan)\n(were against it. They said it's something we can do with five of us.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.2407915704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs023.m4a",
      "text": "（三人とも、BIG4チャレンジで負けてから）\n（これからどうするか必死で考えていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The three of them were desperately trying to figure out)\n(what to do next after losing the BIG4 Challenge.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9333269755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_05-ngs024.m4a",
